    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of the S54-powered icon. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features a factory-spec 8,000 RPM redline, with the double-VANOS system recently overhauled for optimal phase timing and torque delivery. Power is transmitted through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis integrity is flawless, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings to ensure zero structural fatigue. Every mechanical component, from the individual throttle bodies to the cross-drilled rotors, remains in peak operating condition. This is a true turn-key, investment-grade machine with impeccable paint depth and interior upholstery preservation.",
